  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile, pending signature)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 credibility factors are assessed; achieved levels meet or exceed required levels under a conservative MRL-5 interpretation. Decision: Accepted. NOTE: package conforms to ProfileMinimal; signature workflow is pending and no digital signature is present — structural integrity cannot be cryptographically verified (W-SI-01).",
